<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.110.27750>
    bibo:endPage "121" ;
    bibo:journal "PhytoKeys" ;
    bibo:startPage "101" ;
    bibo:volume "110" ;
    dc:creator "Soreng, Robert John; Gillespie, Lynn J." ;
    dc:date "2018" ;
    dc:title "Poa secunda J. Presl (Poaceae): a modern summary of infraspecific taxonomy, chromosome numbers, related species and infrageneric placement based on DNA" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.110.27750.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.110.27750.figure4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.110.27750.figure2> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.110.27750.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Poa secunda habit and panicles: A P. s. subsp. secunda var. secunda (Soreng 9359) B P. s. subsp. juncifolia var. ampla (Soreng 9358) C Panicles of subsp. secunda var. secunda (left) and juncifolia var. ampla (right) (Photos. RJS, Deschutes River near Madras, Jefferson Co., Oregon)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/240276" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.110.27750.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Poa secunda infraspecies illustrations (reproduced from Hitchcock 1935): A P. s. var. ampla panicle and floret B P. s. var. juncifolia panicle and floret C P. s. var. nevadensis panicle and floret D P. s. var. gracillima habit, panicle and floret E P. s. var. scabrella habit, panicles, spikelet and floret F, G P. s. var. secunda habit, panicle and floret variations A, B, C = subsp. juncifolia D, E, F, G = subsp. secunda. Scale bar: 5 mm for florets, 10 mm for spikelet, 5 cm for habits and panicles (10 cm for E habit and panicles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/240279" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.110.27750.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Distribution of Poa secunda subspecies in North America: subsp. secunda (yellow); subsp. juncifolia (blue)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/240277" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

